      "source": "<a href=\"https://sproutsocial.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sprout Social</a>",
      "text": "Here's what happens after you report a possible online crime: \n\n📩 The report is evaluated and referred to the appropriate agency or local law enforcement. \n\n🔎 During an investigation, they may collect evidence, such as electronic devices. \n\n🚔 If there is enough evidence, an arrest is made and potential prosecution may result. \n\nReporting an incident helps stop the harassment and point the victim to survivor support resources.  \n\nLearn more at: https://t.co/CBnlY004QT #Know2Protect",
      "text_resolved": "Here's what happens after you report a possible online crime: \n\n📩 The report is evaluated and referred to the appropriate agency or local law enforcement. \n\n🔎 During an investigation, they may collect evidence, such as electronic devices. \n\n🚔 If there is enough evidence, an arrest is made and potential prosecution may result. \n\nReporting an incident helps stop the harassment and point the victim to survivor support resources.  \n\nLearn more at: http://dhs.gov/know2protect/how-to-report #Know2Protect",
